jibe.sdk.client.events
Class JibeEventService

java.lang.Object
  jibe.sdk.client.JibeServiceBase<IJibeEventService>
      jibe.sdk.client.events.JibeEventService

public class JibeEventService
extends JibeServiceBase<IJibeEventService>

Allows client applications to manage their subscription to specific categories of events. While subscribed, the user will receive that category of events, whenever they occur.

unsubscribe

public void unsubscribe(int category,
                        JibeEventObserver observer)
                 throws JibeServiceException
Unsubscribes the observer from receiving events of the specified category. If the observer was subscribed to other categories of events, it will still receive these other categories of events.

Parameters:
category - The category of events to unsubscribe from, as defined in JibeEvent.Category.
observer - The observer to unsubscribe from observing events of the specified category.
Throws:
JibeServiceException
See Also:
